.''Frequency'' once per day

''Trigger'' You are about to attempt a check to [[Recall Knowledge]].

You call upon the knowledge of Axis to ensure the accuracy of your information. 

You roll a second time and use the higher result. 

If you roll a critical failure, you get a failure instead. If you roll a success, you get a critical success instead.